  "body": "**S3:**S3```json\n{\n  \"$out\": {\n    \"s3\": {\n      \"bucket\": \"<bucket-name>\",\n      \"region\": \"<aws-region>\",\n      \"filename\": \"<file-name>\",\n      \"format\": {\n        \"name\": \"<file-format>\",\n        \"maxFileSize\": \"<file-size>\",\n        \"maxRowGroupSize\": \"<row-group-size>\",\n        \"columnCompression\": \"<compression-type>\"\n      },\n      \"errorMode\": \"stop\"|\"continue\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```**Azure:**Azure```json\n{\n  \"$out\": {\n    \"azure\": {\n      \"serviceURL\": \"<storage-account-url>\",\n      \"containerName\": \"<container-name>\",\n      \"region\": \"<azure-region>\",\n      \"filename\": \"<file-name>\",\n      \"format\": {\n        \"name\": \"<file-format>\",\n        \"maxFileSize\": \"<file-size>\",\n        \"maxRowGroupSize\": \"<row-group-size>\",\n        \"columnCompression\": \"<compression-type>\"\n      },\n      \"errorMode\": \"stop\"|\"continue\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```**Gcp:**GCP```json\n{\n  \"$out\": {\n    \"gcs\": {\n      \"bucket\": \"<bucket-name>\",\n      \"region\": \"<aws-region>\",\n      \"filename\": \"<file-name>\",\n      \"format\": {\n        \"name\": \"<file-format>\",\n        \"maxFileSize\": \"<file-size>\",\n        \"maxRowGroupSize\": \"<row-group-size>\",\n        \"columnCompression\": \"<compression-type>\"\n      },\n      \"errorMode\": \"stop\"|\"continue\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```**Atlas:**Atlas Cluster```json\n{\n  \"$out\": {\n    \"atlas\": {\n      \"projectId\": \"<atlas-project-ID>\",\n      \"clusterName\": \"<atlas-cluster-name>\",\n      \"db\": \"<atlas-database-name>\",\n      \"coll\": \"<atlas-collection-name>\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```",
